          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Commuter Rail Passenger Safety Act </b></p> <p> Amends the Railroad Revitalization and Regulatory Reform Act of 1976 to make the installing of positive train control systems eligible for railroad rehabilitation and improvement direct loans and loan guarantees. </p> <p>Extends the railroad safety technology grants program for FY2016-FY2020.</p>]]></text>
